idge level with their road.}}\n| style=\"background:darkgrey;\" colspan=\"4\"|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 7\n| Amie & Krystle\n| Friends\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:yellow;\"| RISK\n| style=\"background:yellow;\"| RISK\n| style=\"background:salmon;\"| ELIM\n| style=\"background:darkgrey;\" colspan=\"5\"|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 8\n| Manny & Nestor \n| Son & Father\n| style=\"background:yellow;\"| RISK\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:salmon;\"| ELIM\n| style=\"background:darkgrey;\" colspan=\"6\"|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 9\n| Travis & Corey\n| Brothers\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:salmon;\"| ELIM\n| style=\"background:darkgrey;\" colspan=\"7\"|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 10\n| Jessie & Kara\n| Friends\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\"| SAFE\n| style=\"background:salmon;\"| ELIM \n| style=\"background:darkgrey;\" colspan=\"8\"|\n|-\n|}\n\n<sup>\u2020</sup>Team awarded the Golden Brick.<br>\n{{Legend|gold|The team won the challenge.}}\n{{Legend|forestgreen|The team was second this week.}}\n{{Legend|lightgreen|The team was safe from elimination.}}\n{{Legend|yellowgreen|The team was safe due to using the Golden Brick.}}\n{{Legend|yellow|The team was at risk of elimination.}}\n{{Legend|salmon|The team was eliminated from the competition.}}\n;Notes\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Episodes==\n{{Episode table\n| background      = #FEEB39\n| overall         = \n| title           = \n| titleR          = <ref name=\"The Futon Critic\" /><ref name=\"Zap2it\" />\n| airdate         = \n| airdateR        = <ref name=\"The Futon Critic\" /><ref name=\"Zap2it\" />\n| prodcode        = \n| prodcodeR       = <ref name=\"The Futon Critic\" />\n| viewers         = \n| country         = U.S.\n| episodes        = \n\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| Title           = Dream Park The